window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Everyone associates the name Ryker Winchester with money, power plays, negotiations - it's what I'm good at. I always get what I want. </p> <p>I was completely unprepared for Heather. She's a feisty single mom, challenging me in ways no woman ever has. I can't get enough of her. The way she gives in to me is intoxicating, but I need more than hot nights and sexy dates.</p> <p>When she introduces me to her daughter, I fall for that little girl hook, line, and sinker. No one has ever played me for a fool like that kid can do with a single dimpled grin. I want to keep them both.</p> <p>Heather's been hurt before. She's hanging by a thread and doesn't trust easily, but I want more than just some fun.</p> <p>How can I show her that we can build something incredible together?</p>"; 
